@startuml
title 12 - Fluxo Alternativo - Capacidade de Fulfillment Indisponível

autonumber
actor Buyer as Comprador
participant "Marketplace Web" as FE
participant "Marketplace BFF" as BFF
participant "Shipping Promise Service" as Promise
participant "Fulfillment Center Service" as FC
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Routing Service" as Routing
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Order Service" as Order

Comprador -> FE: Solicita cotação com CEP
FE -> BFF: GET /api/web/v1/products/{skuId}/page?zipCode={cep}
BFF -> Promise: POST /shipping-promises/
Promise -> Inventory: POST /inventory/availability/batch
Inventory --> Promise: Estoque disponível
Promise -> FC: POST /fulfillment-centers/candidates/search

alt Nenhum centro com capacidade
  FC --> Promise: []
  Promise --> BFF: available=false, unavailableReason="No fulfillment capacity available"
  BFF --> FE: Shipping indisponível
  FE --> Comprador: Exibe produto sem entrega disponível
else Centro retornado, mas sem janela viável
  FC --> Promise: Candidatos sem janela/cutoff válido
  Promise --> BFF: available=false, unavailableReason="No operational window available"
end

== Falha em reserva de capacidade após pedido ==
Kafka -> Order: CheckoutConfirmedIntegrationEvent
Order -> Kafka: ReserveFulfillmentCapacityCommand
Kafka -> FC: ReserveFulfillmentCapacityCommand
FC -> FC: Capacidade esgotada no slot
FC -> Kafka: FulfillmentCapacityReservationFailedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Order: Falha de reserva de capacidade
Order -> Order: Cancela pedido em saga
Order -> Kafka: ReleaseInventoryReservationCommand
Order -> Kafka: OrderCancelledIntegrationEvent

@enduml
